00:00:00.430 --> 00:00:04.090
OK, endi bizda katta matn bor,
Shriftni o‘zgartirishga o‘tamiz.

00:00:04.090 --> 00:00:07.100
OK, atribut yonidagi katakchalarni 
belgilash orqali matn 

00:00:07.100 --> 00:00:10.850
shriftini o‘zgartirish uchun ishlatiladigan 
atributlarni aniqlashga harakat qiling.

00:00:10.850 --> 00:00:14.020
Buni aniqlagandan so‘ng davom eting va

00:00:14.020 --> 00:00:17.350
avvalgidek, javobni ko‘rish 
uchun SUBMITni bosing.

00:00:17.350 --> 00:00:22.013
Va keyin, ushbu atributlardan foydalanish uchun 
kodni o‘zgartirishga o‘ting

00:00:22.013 --> 00:00:27.360
u ikkala matn ko‘rinishi uchun shrift qiymatini 
 sans serif light deb belgilaydi.

00:00:27.360 --> 00:00:29.970
Tugatganingizdan so‘ng, ekraningiz 
quyidagicha ko‘rinishda bo‘lishi kerak

00:00:29.970 --> 00:00:33.060
bilan nozik sans serif light shriftli
ikkata matn ko‘rinishi.

